### Event Streaming API Tests
### Tests for EventStreamingController endpoints
### Uses {{baseUrl}} from http-client.env.json
### Note: These endpoints return a single JSON object (not a stream)

### Subscribe to session events (returns a JSON Event)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/
Accept: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

> {%
  client.log("Event subscription requested");
%}

### Subscribe to global events (returns a JSON GlobalEvent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/global
Accept: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

> {%
  client.log("Global event subscription requested");
%}
